305
00:26:43,880 --> 00:26:45,300
 Kako će se onda postaviti Trump?

306
00:26:45,300 --> 00:26:48,200
 Hoće li on retorički opet napasti Putina?

307
00:26:48,200 --> 00:26:49,820
 Hoće li dodatno zaoštreti odnose?

308
00:26:49,820 --> 00:26:52,720
 Jer bi ga u tom slučaju Putin u neku ruku ponizio,

309
00:26:52,720 --> 00:26:55,460
